 kitchen and living spaces while rusted steel cladding brings warmth and texture to the modern design.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-210525-710-07.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-210525-710-07-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-210525-710-07-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-210525-710-07-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-210525-710-07-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eLiving room: compact space, expansive feel\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDespite its modest size, the living room feels spacious and composed. Clean lines, warm wood cabinetry, and a restrained color palette keep the focus on texture and form. A deep white sectional and rug add comfort and personality, while sculptural accents and curated details bring the space to life without clutter.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-08.jpg\" alt=\"This cozy living room blends earthy textures and warm wood tones with expansive glass walls that open to lush bamboo landscaping. A colorful rug and sculptural furnishings add comfort and character to the modern minimalist space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-08.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-08-940x752.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-08-800x