lass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12.jpg\" alt=\"This cozy living room blends earthy textures and warm wood tones with expansive glass walls that open to lush bamboo landscaping. A colorful rug and sculptural furnishings add comfort and character to the modern minimalist space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12-940x626.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-12-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13.jpg\" alt=\"This cozy living room blends earthy textures and warm wood tones with expansive glass walls that open to lush bamboo landscaping. A colorful rug and sculptural furnishings add comfort and character to the modern minimalist space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-210525-710-13-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14.jpg\" alt=\"A metal bar unit displays wine bottles and glassware with effortless style, paired with a sculptural round mirror. Warm wood finishes and soft textures in the background create a cozy yet refined living space.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-living-room-bar-210525-710-14-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eKitchen + dining: minimal, efficient, warm\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe kitchen is sleek and deeply integrated into the architecture. Wood cabinetry wraps around the space, hiding appliances and creating a warm, seamless visual flow. The backsplash is lined with muted green tiles, offering a soft contrast to the wood and echoing the home’s connection to nature. A crisp white island anchors the room and is completed with olive-toned stools.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTucked just off the kitchen is a built-in dining nook in an intimate, wood-wrapped alcove that feels both cozy and tailored. The velvet-textured bench seats and floating wood table offer a quiet place for meals, conversation, or work, with a pendant globe casting a soft glow overhead.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1279\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15.jpg\" alt=\"Rich wood cabinetry sets a warm tone in this modern kitchen, where clean white countertops and olive-toned backsplash tiles add depth. A built-in breakfast nook doubles as a cozy workspace, blending form and function beautifully.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15-940x626.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-15-1536x1023.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16.jpg\" alt=\"Rich wood cabinetry sets a warm tone in this modern kitchen, where clean white countertops and olive-toned backsplash tiles add depth. A built-in breakfast nook doubles as a cozy workspace, blending form and function beautifully.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-kitchen-210525-710-16-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17.jpg\" alt=\"Rich wood cabinetry sets a warm tone in this modern kitchen, where clean white countertops and olive-toned backsplash tiles add depth. A built-in breakfast nook doubles as a cozy workspace, blending form and function beautifully.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17.jpg 1600w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-booth-dining-210525-710-17-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eBedroom: compact comfort with connection to green\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bedroom feels like a private retreat, wrapped in warm textures and natural light. A full-height glass wall opens to the courtyard, bringing in greenery and soft daylight while keeping the space serene and secluded. Thoughtful details like grasscloth wallpaper and built-in shelving add quiet sophistication.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18.jpg\" alt=\"This serene bedroom blends soft textures with sleek lines, opening to a tranquil courtyard garden. Floor-to-ceiling glass draws nature inward, while warm wood floors and grasscloth walls ground the space in quiet luxury.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bedroom-210525-710-18-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eBathroom: rich materiality and luxury\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathroom balances rich materiality with openness and light. A wood double vanity with matte black fixtures anchors the space, paired with full-height mirrors and globe lights that reflect natural light throughout. The shower, lined in dark mosaic tile, has views of a small private courtyard, where plants and corrugated metal create a serene, spa-like backdrop. It’s a space that feels both grounded and quietly luxurious.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1474\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19.jpg\" alt=\"Clean lines and earthy textures define this spa-like bathroom. The floating walnut vanity and matte black fixtures feel warm yet modern, while a glass shower opens to a private garden framed by vertical cedar slats.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19-940x722.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19-800x614.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19-768x590.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-19-1536x1179.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1479\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-20.jpg\" alt=\"This moody double shower pairs rich mosaic tile with a glass wall that opens to a minimalist courtyard. The balance of dark texture and natural light gives the space a grounded, spa-like feel.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-20.jpg 1400w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-20-940x993.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-20-800x845.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-glass-walls-bathroom-210525-710-20-768x811.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere are the architectural drawings that guided the design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1483\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a modern home with a corrugated steel exterior and an interior courtyard.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21-940x726.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21-800x618.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21-768x593.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-21-1536x1186.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1483\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a modern home with a corrugated steel exterior and an interior courtyards.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22-940x726.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22-800x618.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22-768x593.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-22-1536x1186.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1261\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a modern home with a corrugated steel exterior and an interior courtyards.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23-940x617.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23-800x525.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23-768x504.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-23-1536x1009.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1766\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings for a modern home with a corrugated steel exterior and an interior courtyards.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24-940x865.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24-800x736.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24-768x706.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/modern-house-architectural-drawings-210525-713-24-1536x1413.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Stealth House feels calm by design, a quiet retreat shaped by intention. More than a home, it’s a model for urban living that values privacy, sustainability, and thoughtful use of space.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://leonidfurmansky.com/\"\u003eLeonid Furmanski\u003c/a\u003e | Architect: Specht Novak | Builder: Smock Build\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
